							my profile!</h4>
					</div>
				</div>
				<%
				if (request.getParameter("errCode") == null) {
				} else if (request.getParameter("errCode").equals("passwordsDoNotMatch")) {
				%>
				<p style="color: red">Password do not match!</p>
				<%
